data.description: JUST REDUCED! This home located only 30 minutes from beautiful downtown Austin, features 3-beds, 2-baths and spans a total of 1,368 sq. ft. The primary bedroom features an en-suite bathroom with a walk-in shower and a tub, complimented by a roomy walk-in closet. Two additional bedrooms offer flexibility for office space or guest bedrooms that share a full bathroom. The layout includes a practical laundry room, and the two-car garage provides secure parking and storage. Designed for modern living, this home combines functionality with simplicity. Contact us to schedule a viewing!
